{
  "video_id": "4XYgx805_88",
  "title": "What The 2019 Oscar Nominees Looked Like Behind The Scenes | Movies Insider",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 187.0,
      "end_time": 1187.0,
      "text": "Off we go."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 4470.0,
      "end_time": 6290.0,
      "text": "Narrator: This year's Oscars won't include"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 6300.0,
      "end_time": 9400.0,
      "text": "a Popular Film category, like the Academy once proposed."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 9400.0,
      "end_time": 11800.0,
      "text": "But, many of your favorites will still be there."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 12740.0,
      "end_time": 15570.0,
      "text": "Campaigning for an Oscar takes a lot of work"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 15570.0,
      "end_time": 17100.0,
      "text": "but nothing like the work that went"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 17100.0,
      "end_time": 19000.0,
      "text": "into actually making the movie."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 19000.0,
      "end_time": 21140.0,
      "text": "From groundbreaking visual effects"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 21140.0,
      "end_time": 24290.0,
      "text": "to daring stunts, to layers of makeup"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 24290.0,
      "end_time": 27220.0,
      "text": "there's a lot to admire from this year's Oscar nominees."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 27220.0,
      "end_time": 29410.0,
      "text": "Here's what 2019 Oscar nominees"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 29410.0,
      "end_time": 30963.0,
      "text": "looked like behind the scenes."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 42570.0,
      "end_time": 45900.0,
      "text": "Few movies in the last decade have altered our culture"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 45900.0,
      "end_time": 49700.0,
      "text": "as much as Black Panther did in 2018."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 49700.0,
      "end_time": 50640.0,
      "text": "Its showing at the Oscars proves"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 50640.0,
      "end_time": 54120.0,
      "text": "that it took blockbuster filmmaking to new heights."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 54120.0,
      "end_time": 56720.0,
      "text": "The movie involves a lot of demanding stunt work"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 56720.0,
      "end_time": 59610.0,
      "text": "from the cast for each intense fight scene."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 59610.0,
      "end_time": 62519.0,
      "text": "Yes, Danai Gurira really did use a wig"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 62520.0,
      "end_time": 66134.0,
      "text": "as a defense mechanism. And yes, Chadwick Boseman"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 66134.0,
      "end_time": 70990.0,
      "text": "did kick a guy across a field, with the help of a few wires."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 70990.0,
      "end_time": 74240.0,
      "text": "Meanwhile, Michael B. Jordan went to set every day"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 74240.0,
      "end_time": 77809.0,
      "text": "and was covered in around 3,000 prosthetic dots."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 77810.0,
      "end_time": 79760.0,
      "text": "Makeup artist Joel Harlow told us"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 79760.0,
      "end_time": 81620.0,
      "text": "the fake scars were made to withstand"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 81620.0,
      "end_time": 83750.0,
      "text": "the actor's more physical scenes"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 83750.0,
      "end_time": 85713.0,
      "text": "as well as the ones where he got wet."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 86650.0,
      "end_time": 87970.0,
      "text": "And a studio in Atlanta"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 87970.0,
      "end_time": 91150.0,
      "text": "was convincingly transformed into Wakanda."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 91150.0,
      "end_time": 94510.0,
      "text": "That space came complete with bustling city streets"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 94510.0,
      "end_time": 97343.0,
      "text": "and a waterfall that would become Warrior Falls."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 111850.0,
      "end_time": 115220.0,
      "text": "Horror movies are often overlooked during awards season"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 115220.0,
      "end_time": 117560.0,
      "text": "but this box office and critical success"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 117560.0,
      "end_time": 120173.0,
      "text": "was too impressive for the Oscars to ignore."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 121800.0,
      "end_time": 124410.0,
      "text": "While the movie produced scares from its lack of sound"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 124410.0,
      "end_time": 127500.0,
      "text": "the ways it did use sound were impressive."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 127500.0,
      "end_time": 129610.0,
      "text": "The film's sound team used a strange array"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 129610.00000000001,
      "end_time": 131513.0,
      "text": "of objects to make Foley sounds."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 133560.0,
      "end_time": 136900.0,
      "text": "Crab legs perfectly captured the sound"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 136900.0,
      "end_time": 137870.0,
      "text": "of the monsters walking."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 137870.0,
      "end_time": 141740.0,
      "text": "A combination of celery and romaine lettuce"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 141740.0,
      "end_time": 144510.0,
      "text": "would make the sound of an ear opening."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 144510.0,
      "end_time": 146453.0,
      "text": "To figure out the monsters' spine-chilling"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 146512.0,
      "end_time": 149942.0,
      "text": "echolocation sounds, the team did some experimenting"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 150000.0,
      "end_time": 152170.0,
      "text": "and discovered the best way to do it"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 152170.0,
      "end_time": 154720.0,
      "text": "was by tasering a patch of grapes"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 154720.0,
      "end_time": 156443.0,
      "text": "and then slowing the sound down."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 172390.0,
      "end_time": 176102.0,
      "text": "There'll always be a place for period pieces at the Oscars."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 177240.0,
      "end_time": 180540.0,
      "text": "The historical epic, centering around Mary Queen of Scots"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 180540.0,
      "end_time": 183720.0,
      "text": "and Queen Elizabeth I, and starring Margot Robbie"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 183720.0,
      "end_time": 186981.0,
      "text": "and Saoirse Ronan, is notable for its costumes"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 186981.0,
      "end_time": 190403.0,
      "text": "makeup, hairpieces, and sets."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 192310.0,
      "end_time": 194800.0,
      "text": "The movie was shot on location"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 194800.0,
      "end_time": 196380.0,
      "text": "around the United Kingdom and Scotland."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 196380.0,
      "end_time": 199823.0,
      "text": "The stars acted with a literal army of extras."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 213360.0,
      "end_time": 215690.0,
      "text": "The Favourite plays a bit more fast and loose"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 215690.0,
      "end_time": 218600.0,
      "text": "with history, but it still flawlessly immerses"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 218600.0,
      "end_time": 221853.0,
      "text": "the audience in 18th-century British aristocratic life."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 222760.0,
      "end_time": 225912.0,
      "text": "The costumes and wigs are eye-popping and elaborate."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 227410.0,
      "end_time": 230560.0,
      "text": "The movie was shot at Hatfield House in England."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 230560.0,
      "end_time": 233720.0,
      "text": "They stripped many of the beautiful rooms in the palace"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 233720.0,
      "end_time": 237453.0,
      "text": "and built a massive bath, as well as Abigail's room."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 251740.0,
      "end_time": 253910.0,
      "text": "The reception of First Man, which chronicles"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 253910.0,
      "end_time": 257260.0,
      "text": "Neil Armstrong's trip to the moon, was mixed."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 257260.0,
      "end_time": 259100.0,
      "text": "But one thing nobody can deny"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 259100.00000000003,
      "end_time": 260873.00000000003,
      "text": "is that it's visually stunning."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 262770.0,
      "end_time": 266460.0,
      "text": "Its set pieces are as historically accurate as possible."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 266460.0,
      "end_time": 268690.0,
      "text": "Production designer Nathan Crowley told us"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 268690.0,
      "end_time": 271350.0,
      "text": "that the lunar module and space capsule"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 271350.0,
      "end_time": 272930.0,
      "text": "were built to scale."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 272930.0,
      "end_time": 276100.0,
      "text": "Meanwhile, the Saturn V model seen in the movie"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 276100.0,
      "end_time": 278830.0,
      "text": "was actually just 14 feet tall."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 278830.0,
      "end_time": 282990.0,
      "text": "That's about 1/25th the size of the actual rocket."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 282990.0,
      "end_time": 285320.0,
      "text": "Some of the models could even move."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 285320.0,
      "end_time": 289280.0,
      "text": "In some scenes, to convincingly replicate zero gravity"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 289280.0,
      "end_time": 291929.0,
      "text": "they put the camera below the actors."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 291930.0,
      "end_time": 295283.0,
      "text": "A technique that has been used in many movies set in space."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 298550.0,
      "end_time": 301750.0,
      "text": "The moon landing sequence, which is shot in IMAX"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 301750.0,
      "end_time": 305900.0,
      "text": "will actually make you feel like you're walking on the moon."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 305900.0,
      "end_time": 308600.0,
      "text": "Some parts of this sequence were shot in a quarry."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 308600.0,
      "end_time": 309310.0,
      "text": "Other parts were shot on"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 309310.0,
      "end_time": 311773.0,
      "text": "a very convincing-looking soundstage."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 313150.0,
      "end_time": 315409.0,
      "text": "The stunts were equally impressive."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 315410.0,
      "end_time": 317280.0,
      "text": "Gosling allowed himself to be launched"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 317280.0,
      "end_time": 321100.0,
      "text": "out of a capsule, and then got dragged around"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 321100.0,
      "end_time": 322933.0,
      "text": "in the movie's most daring stunt."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 343120.0,
      "end_time": 345220.0,
      "text": "What sets A Star is Born apart is that"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 345220.0,
      "end_time": 347560.0,
      "text": "all the concert scenes were filmed live"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 347560.0,
      "end_time": 349740.0,
      "text": "and Bradley Cooper and Lady Gaga"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 349740.0,
      "end_time": 352130.0,
      "text": "are always performing together."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 352130.0,
      "end_time": 354740.0,
      "text": "Even for two people as talented as them"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 354740.0,
      "end_time": 356833.0,
      "text": "they still had to rehearse a lot."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 358440.0,
      "end_time": 361430.0,
      "text": "A big part of the production was sound editing"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 361430.0,
      "end_time": 363630.0,
      "text": "which required layering multiple sounds"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 363630.0,
      "end_time": 366130.0,
      "text": "in a single scene, including the vocals."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 366130.0,
      "end_time": 367953.0,
      "text": "All of which were sung live."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 383180.0,
      "end_time": 385740.0,
      "text": "Wes Anderson's second stop-motion animated feature"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 385740.0,
      "end_time": 389130.0,
      "text": "was one of the best animated movies of 2018."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 389130.0,
      "end_time": 390670.0,
      "text": "It's staggering just to look at"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 390670.0,
      "end_time": 392610.0,
      "text": "the numbers behind the movie."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 392610.0,
      "end_time": 394550.0,
      "text": "Isle of Dogs animators were working with"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 394550.0,
      "end_time": 399200.0,
      "text": "around 1,105 puppets on set."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 399200.0,
      "end_time": 401800.0,
      "text": "A single sushi making sequence from the movie"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 401800.0,
      "end_time": 403673.0,
      "text": "took six to eight months to bring to life."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 404860.0,
      "end_time": 408270.0,
      "text": "Animators, meanwhile, had to use pins and wooden sticks"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 408270.0,
      "end_time": 410640.0,
      "text": "to move the dogs' eyeballs and lips around"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 410640.0,
      "end_time": 413360.0,
      "text": "to make the characters move realistically."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 413360.0,
      "end_time": 416920.0,
      "text": "The animators even painstakingly moved the fur around"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 416920.0,
      "end_time": 418690.0,
      "text": "to give the impression that dog's fur"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 418690.0,
      "end_time": 420960.0,
      "text": "was blowing in the wind."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 420960.0,
      "end_time": 424219.0,
      "text": "Stop-motion animation requires faces to get changed out"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 424220.0,
      "end_time": 426870.0,
      "text": "for each different mood and emotion."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 426870.0,
      "end_time": 430310.0,
      "text": "Andy Gent, the head of the movie's puppet department"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 430310.0,
      "end_time": 432720.0,
      "text": "told us that the character's fur made this process"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 432720.0,
      "end_time": 434463.0,
      "text": "much more difficult than usual."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 448960.0,
      "end_time": 450979.0,
      "text": "Marvel's most ambitious movie yet"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 450980.0,
      "end_time": 454150.0,
      "text": "didn't quite get the same awards love as Black Panther"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 454150.0,
      "end_time": 456729.0,
      "text": "but it still managed to make an appearance."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 456730.0,
      "end_time": 458830.0,
      "text": "The biggest standout technical aspect"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 458830.0,
      "end_time": 461409.0,
      "text": "of the latest Avengers was Josh Brolin's"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 461410.0,
      "end_time": 464300.0,
      "text": "towering performance as Thanos."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 464300.0,
      "end_time": 467130.0,
      "text": "The actor performed in a motion capture suit"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 467130.0,
      "end_time": 470600.0,
      "text": "for a character who would then be created using CGI."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 470600.0,
      "end_time": 473820.0,
      "text": "Because Thanos is so tall, Brolin often acted"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 473820.0,
      "end_time": 476140.0,
      "text": "with an object on top of his head."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 476140.0,
      "end_time": 478400.0,
      "text": "That way, actors would know where exactly"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 478400.0,
      "end_time": 479549.0,
      "text": "they should be looking."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 480420.0,
      "end_time": 483700.0,
      "text": "Motion-capture technology has gotten so good"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 483700.0,
      "end_time": 486140.0,
      "text": "that Thanos felt real."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 486140.0,
      "end_time": 488930.0,
      "text": "Honestly, it's about time the Academy starts taking"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 488930.0,
      "end_time": 491800.0,
      "text": "motion-capture performances more seriously."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 507480.0,
      "end_time": 509550.0,
      "text": "The long-awaited sequel involved"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 509550.0,
      "end_time": 512400.0,
      "text": "a cast of very committed actors."
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 512400.0,
      "end_time": 514819.0,
      "text": "Meanwhile, production designers created"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 514820.00000000006,
      "end_time": 519263.00000000006,
      "text": "a very accurate version of 1930s London inside a studio."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 521200.00000000006,
      "end_time": 524829.0,
      "text": "For this shot, in which Mary Poppins falls into a bathtub"
    },
